4. Prerequisites
On the Ansible Machine
Install Ansible and required tools:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install ansible curl tar -y
Verify installation:
ansible --version

5. Download RKE2 Air-Gap Artifacts
Create directory for artifacts:
mkdir -p ~/ansible-airgap/files/rke2-airgap
cd ~/ansible-airgap/files/rke2-airgap
Download required files from the RKE2 release page.
Required files:
install.sh
rke2.linux-amd64.tar.gz
rke2-images.linux-amd64.tar.zst
sha256sum-amd64.txt
These files allow RKE2 installation without internet access.
Final directory structure:
files/rke2-airgap/
├── install.sh
├── rke2.linux-amd64.tar.gz
├── rke2-images.linux-amd64.tar.zst
└── sha256sum-amd64.txt

